&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking for a Bank Registered Nurse (Hospice at Home) &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Based in the Community&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re recruiting bank nurses to join our friendly well established Hospice at Home team. We deliver the highest standard of palliative care for patients in their own home.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join our multidisciplinary Community Team and help us to provide the best standard of palliative nursing care and support to patients and families. We’re looking for candidates with excellent communication skills, a passion for palliative care, a can do attitude and a desire to make a real difference to the lives of patients and their families. Community and palliative care experience preferable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A full UK driving license and your own vehicle is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
